than I'd like to admit.

00:04:17.757 --> 00:04:21.344 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO] Hey, hey! You guys,
we're right over here!

00:04:21.428 --> 00:04:26.808 position:50% align:center
Hey! Good morning,
Erika! Usagihara!

00:04:26.891 --> 00:04:27.851 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
Morning.

00:04:27.934 --> 00:04:29.019 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Morning.

00:04:29.102 --> 00:04:30.520 position:50% align:center
Wow, you guys look
pretty different

00:04:30.603 --> 00:04:31.771 position:50% align:center
