You look super cute!

00:04:42.449 --> 00:04:44.159 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Thanks, you look cute, too!

00:04:44.242 --> 00:04:45.326 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:48.246 position:50% align:center
