a little effort into it.

00:04:51.833 --> 00:04:53.418 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
And your nails are awesome!

00:04:53.501 --> 00:04:54.669 position:50% align:center
Thank you!

00:04:54.753 --> 00:04:57.172 position:50% align:center
That'll only be
for today, though.

00:04:57.255 --> 00:04:59.215 position:50% align:center
And just look at you, Komichi.

00:04:59.299 --> 00:05:01.468 position:50% align:center
--[KOMICHI] Huh?
--Your hair.

00:05:01.551 --> 00:05:04.346 position:50% align:center
[gasps] So, you can tell?

00:05:04.429 --> 00:05:06.514 position:50% align:center
Your bangs are
a little shorter now.

00:05:06.598 --> 00:05:08.016 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI giggles]

