the things we'll need.

00:05:17.192 --> 00:05:18.568 position:50% align:center
Vinyl tape for the cheer squad,

00:05:18.651 --> 00:05:20.987 position:50% align:center
and some cloth to make
all the class flags,

00:05:21.071 --> 00:05:23.615 position:50% align:center
