necessities like that.

00:05:23.698 --> 00:05:25.992 position:50% align:center
There's a directory
right over there.

00:05:26.076 --> 00:05:27.911 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Leave it to me!

00:05:27.994 --> 00:05:31.748 position:50% align:center
It'd be my pleasure to be your
guide through this mall today!

00:05:37.045 --> 00:05:40.757 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] Wow. It's almost
like an amusement park.

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.634 position:50% align:center
So cool. I've never
actually shopped

00:05:42.717 --> 00:05:44.386 position:50% align:center
