your wrist for luck.

00:12:21.282 --> 00:12:22.617 position:50% align:center
Oh, how cool!

00:12:22.701 --> 00:12:23.993 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO] Yeah. You wear
them when you have

00:12:24.077 --> 00:12:26.204 position:50% align:center
something you're wishing for.

00:12:26.287 --> 00:12:28.289 position:50% align:center
And they say, when it
falls off on its own,

00:12:28.373 --> 00:12:30.959 position:50% align:center
then it's a sign that your
wish is about to come true.

00:12:31.042 --> 00:12:32.335 position:50% align:center
Kizaki and I thought
we could maybe

00:12:32.419 --> 00:12:33.795 position:50% align:center
use them in the festival

00:12:33.878 --> 00:12:36.339 position:50% align:center
to help bring us together
during the competition.

00:12:36.423 --> 00:12:39.175 position:50% align:center
Everyone gets a matching
bracelet to wear!

00:12:41.553 --> 00:12:43.513 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Mm!

00:12:45.557 --> 00:12:46.474 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:12:46.558 --> 00:12:48.685 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO, TOMONO, KOMICHI giggle]

00:12:53.314 --> 00:12:55.483 position:50% align:center
It's good.

00:12:55.567 --> 00:12:58.069 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:12:58.153 --> 00:12:59.988 position:50% align:center
Erika! You're just too cute!

00:13:00.071 --> 00:13:01.197 position:50% align:center
[GROUP laughing]

00:13:01.281 --> 00:13:04.951 position:50% align:center
Oh, jeez. Don't make
it a big deal.

00:13:05.035 --> 00:13:07.662 position:50% align:center
Well, anyway, that was our idea.

00:13:07.746 --> 00:13:10.081 position:50% align:center
Why don't we all work on making
the bracelets together?

00:13:10.165 --> 00:13:11.416 position:50% align:center
Later, at the dorm?

00:13:11.499 --> 00:13:12.625 position:50% align:center
I'm so in!

00:13:12.709 --> 00:13:15.420 position:50% align:center
How fun! I haven't been
to the dorms before.

00:13:15.503 --> 00:13:17.422 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Okay! Now that that's decided,

00:13:17.505 --> 00:13:19.549 position:50% align:center
let's see when
the bus is coming.

00:13:19.632 --> 00:13:21.676 position:50% align:center
Oh, Kizaki.

00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:24.596 position:50% align:center
Let me give you that book
right now, before I forget.

00:13:24.679 --> 00:13:26.056 position:50% align:center
Great, thank you!

00:13:27.724 --> 00:13:29.017 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Huh?

00:13:34.356 --> 00:13:36.441 position:50% align:center
Something wrong?

00:13:36.524 --> 00:13:38.818 position:50% align:center
Are you okay?

00:13:38.902 --> 00:13:42.989 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] It's gone.
My special bookmark is gone.

00:14:32.622 --> 00:14:34.040 position:50% align:center
Have any luck?

00:14:34.124 --> 00:14:36.167 position:50% align:center
I didn't see it anywhere.

00:14:36.251 --> 00:14:37.419 position:50% align:center
That's a bummer.

00:14:37.502 --> 00:14:41.131 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Yes. Okay.

00:14:41.214 --> 00:14:44.801 position:50% align:center
I see. Well, thank you.

00:14:44.884 --> 00:14:46.761 position:50% align:center
Anything?

00:14:46.845 --> 00:14:49.180 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO] No one has
brought in any lost items.

00:14:49.264 --> 00:14:50.765 position:50% align:center
And the bus is
back at the depot,

00:14:50.849 --> 00:14:54.853 position:50% align:center
but they didn't find it there.

00:14:54.936 --> 00:14:57.522 position:50% align:center
Then, it has to be
here in the mall.

00:14:57.605 --> 00:14:59.733 position:50% align:center
I'll go look around
one more time.

00:14:59.816 --> 00:15:02.819 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Oh, don't worry about it.

00:15:02.902 --> 00:15:05.280 position:50% align:center
I mean, I really have been
using that thing forever,

00:15:05.363 --> 00:15:08.283 position:50% align:center
so maybe it's just time
to get a new one.

00:15:08.366 --> 00:15:10.577 position:50% align:center
Sorry for dragging
you all into this.

00:15:10.660 --> 00:15:12.245 position:50% align:center
And anyway, the bus to the dorm

00:15:12.328 --> 00:15:13.872 position:50% align:center
should be here pretty
soon, shouldn't it?

00:15:13.955 --> 00:15:17.375 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Uh. Yeah, it should, but--

00:15:17.459 --> 00:15:19.336 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Then let's get going.

00:15:29.387 --> 00:15:30.180 position:50% align:center
The bookmark!

00:15:30.263 --> 00:15:31.639 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:15:33.224 --> 00:15:34.059 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:15:34.142 --> 00:15:35.560 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
We found it!

00:15:37.771 --> 00:15:40.940 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] That's where we
were talking this morning.

00:15:41.024 --> 00:15:42.317 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.194 position:50% align:center
Look at that! Someone
must've tied it to a balloon

00:15:44.277 --> 00:15:46.696 position:50% align:center
to make it easier to see!
Wasn't that nice?

00:15:46.780 --> 00:15:49.532 position:50% align:center
Whew! Well, that's
a huge relief!

00:15:49.616 --> 00:15:51.034 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Sorry about this.

00:15:51.117 --> 00:15:53.787 position:50% align:center
I must've dropped it when
I pulled out my notebook.

00:15:59.834 --> 00:16:01.044 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO gasps]

00:16:11.179 --> 00:16:12.472 position:50% align:center
[PRINCIPAL 9A]
The gold medal winner

00:16:12.555 --> 00:16:15.725 position:50% align:center
of the 34th Annual Elementary
School Essay Contest

00:16:15.809 --> 00:16:17.811 position:50% align:center
is Miss Tomono Kojou.

00:16:17.894 --> 00:16:22.899 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO panting]

00:16:33.910 --> 00:16:35.203 position:50% align:center
Guess what, Mom?

00:16:35.286 --> 00:16:38.832 position:50% align:center
I think I wanna write books
someday, when I grow up!

00:16:47.340 --> 00:16:49.759 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
All right, tree to the rescue!

00:16:49.843 --> 00:16:51.011 position:50% align:center
Yeah, but--

00:16:56.474 --> 00:16:59.269 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO grunting]

00:17:07.694 --> 00:17:09.320 position:50% align:center
Okay, now climb on!

00:17:11.072 --> 00:17:13.533 position:50% align:center
You mean, on your back?

00:17:13.616 --> 00:17:14.784 position:50% align:center
On my shoulders!

00:17:14.868 --> 00:17:17.370 position:50% align:center
[yelps] No way! I'm too heavy!

00:17:17.454 --> 00:17:19.873 position:50% align:center
You'd totally
end up getting hurt!

00:17:19.956 --> 00:17:21.374 position:50% align:center
I know!

00:17:26.588 --> 00:17:29.382 position:50% align:center
And you're positive
that this is safe?

00:17:29.466 --> 00:17:32.010 position:50% align:center
--[KOMICHI] Mm-hm.
--Yeah, girl!

00:17:32.093 --> 00:17:33.762 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Well, okay.

00:17:36.097 --> 00:17:37.891 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Sorry I'm so heavy.

00:17:37.974 --> 00:17:39.017 position:50% align:center
Let's do this!

00:17:39.100 --> 00:17:40.393 position:50% align:center
--[ERIKA] Right!
--[TOUKO] Okay!

00:17:41.603 --> 00:17:43.730 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Ready, go!

00:17:43.813 --> 00:17:45.106 position:50% align:center
[yelps]

00:17:47.567 --> 00:17:48.735 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:17:53.823 --> 00:17:55.784 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Move forward a little!

00:17:55.867 --> 00:17:57.160 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI, ERIKA, TOUKO]
'Kay!

00:17:58.912 --> 00:18:00.372 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
That's good!

00:18:06.252 --> 00:18:08.296 position:50% align:center
You can do it! Almost there!

00:18:11.549 --> 00:18:12.801 position:50% align:center
No, I can't.

00:18:12.884 --> 00:18:15.095 position:50% align:center
I guess we're still
not high enough.

00:18:15.178 --> 00:18:17.597 position:50% align:center
Come on, we're so close.

00:18:19.974 --> 00:18:21.726 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Just a little higher.

00:18:22.769 --> 00:18:25.689 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI gasps]
Let's try it again, Kojou!

00:18:25.772 --> 00:18:26.981 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:18:30.443 --> 00:18:32.821 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Uh, I don't know about this.

00:18:32.904 --> 00:18:36.116 position:50% align:center
Don't worry! I promise
we'll catch you!

00:18:41.663 --> 00:18:42.706 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Usagihara!

00:18:42.789 --> 00:18:43.915 position:50% align:center
All set!

00:18:43.998 --> 00:18:44.874 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Erika!

00:18:44.958 --> 00:18:46.876 position:50% align:center
Yeah!

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:47.877 position:50% align:center
Let's go!

00:18:47.961 --> 00:18:50.088 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA, KOMICHI, TOUKO]
Ready. Up!

00:19:00.557 --> 00:19:01.766 position:50% align:center
I got it!

00:19:16.906 --> 00:19:18.575 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Thanks, you guys!

00:19:19.659 --> 00:19:21.911 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO] Man, that was
a close call, huh?

00:19:21.995 --> 00:19:23.329 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] You're the one
who suggested doing it

00:19:23.413 --> 00:19:25.331 position:50% align:center
like a mock cavalry battle.

00:19:25.415 --> 00:19:28.126 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO] Well, I'd say Akebi's
idea was a lot more surprising!

00:19:28.209 --> 00:19:30.962 position:50% align:center
It really is such
a beautiful bookmark.

00:19:32.756 --> 00:19:34.632 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
At least it all worked out!

00:19:35.675 --> 00:19:38.386 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] You know, when I saw
you looking up at that balloon,

00:19:38.470 --> 00:19:40.305 position:50% align:center
it kinda felt like
all your happy feelings

00:19:40.388 --> 00:19:44.225 position:50% align:center
were flying away along with it.

00:19:44.309 --> 00:19:46.561 position:50% align:center
I'm so glad we got it back!

00:19:46.644 --> 00:19:49.606 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Thank you so much!

00:19:52.901 --> 00:19:56.029 position:50% align:center
Huh? Yikes!

00:19:58.740 --> 00:19:59.741 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Oh, jeez.

00:19:59.824 --> 00:20:01.534 position:50% align:center
I didn't think to
bring my umbrella.

00:20:01.618 --> 00:20:02.744 position:50% align:center
Me neither.

00:20:02.827 --> 00:20:05.080 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
I do have mine, but...

00:20:06.081 --> 00:20:08.416 position:50% align:center
Yeah, unfortunately,
I think the bus stop

00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:10.752 position:50% align:center
is a bit of a walk from here.

00:20:10.835 --> 00:20:14.756 position:50% align:center
Well, maybe we should
wait for the next one.

00:20:14.839 --> 00:20:16.758 position:50% align:center
I guess so.

00:20:16.841 --> 00:20:19.094 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
Wait, where's Akebi?

00:20:19.177 --> 00:20:20.637 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
Huh?

00:20:25.517 --> 00:20:27.852 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:20:27.936 --> 00:20:28.978 position:50% align:center
Look, you guys!

00:20:29.062 --> 00:20:33.817 position:50% align:center
Even in the rain,
it's still floating!

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:38.238 position:50% align:center
Oh, my gosh! That girl
is something else!

00:20:38.321 --> 00:20:40.323 position:50% align:center
You know, when I watch Akebi,

00:20:40.407 --> 00:20:41.908 position:50% align:center
it kind of makes me
wanna write a book

00:20:41.991 --> 00:20:44.369 position:50% align:center
with a character just like her.

00:20:48.248 --> 00:20:50.959 position:50% align:center
[TOMONO]
I think she's pretty incredible.

00:20:51.042 --> 00:20:52.627 position:50% align:center
Jeez!

00:20:54.337 --> 00:20:55.588 position:50% align:center
Hey, wait for me!

00:20:55.672 --> 00:20:56.715 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:56.798 --> 00:21:01.678 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI, TOUKO, ERIKA laughing]

00:21:01.761 --> 00:21:02.929 position:50% align:center
Wait up!

00:21:04.431 --> 00:21:06.599 position:50% align:center
Race to the bus stop!
What do ya say?

00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:14.107 position:50% align:center
[ALL yelling, laughing]

00:21:14.190 --> 00:21:15.400 position:50% align:center
Love it!

00:21:15.483 --> 00:21:17.110 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:21:17.193 --> 00:21:19.112 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:21:51.519 --> 00:21:54.939 position:50% align:center
Looks like the rain stopped.

00:21:55.023 --> 00:21:57.567 position:50% align:center
Guess it was just
a passing shower.

00:22:03.281 --> 00:22:05.200 position:50% align:center
Oh! Look at the sky!

00:22:11.331 --> 00:22:13.041 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
It's the pipe organ!

00:22:14.042 --> 00:22:21.383 position:50% align:center
[ALL laugh]